Event.Message: WCN has started a new session. Peer UUID: %2 Connect reason: %3 Session GUID: %1
Event.Template: <template xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/win/2004/08/events"> <data name="SessionGuid" inType="win:GUID" outType="xs:GUID"/> <data name="PeerUuid" inType="win:GUID" outType="xs:GUID"/> <data name="Trigger" inType="win:UInt32" outType="xs:unsignedInt"/> </template>

Event.Message: WCN has established a connection. Session GUID: %1
WCN is preparing to parse a message. Session GUID: %1 Message: %3
Event.Template: <template xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/win/2004/08/events"> <data name="SessionGuid" inType="win:GUID" outType="xs:GUID"/> <data name="MessageGuid" inType="win:GUID" outType="xs:GUID"/> <data name="MessageBlobLength" inType="win:UInt16" outType="xs:unsignedShort"/> <data name="MessageBlob" inType="win:Binary" outType="xs:hexBinary" length="MessageBlobLength"/> </template>

Event.Message: WCN has generated a message. Session GUID: %1 Message: %3
Event.Template: <template xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/win/2004/08/events"> <data name="SessionGuid" inType="win:GUID" outType="xs:GUID"/> <data name="MessageGuid" inType="win:GUID" outType="xs:GUID"/> <data name="MessageBlobLength" inType="win:UInt16" outType="xs:unsignedShort"/> <data name="MessageBlob" inType="win:Binary" outType="xs:hexBinary" length="MessageBlobLength"/> </template>

Event.Message: WCN has completed a session successfully. Session GUID: %1
WCN failed to complete a session. Session GUID: %1 Error code: %2
Event.Template: <template xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/win/2004/08/events"> <data name="SessionGuid" inType="win:GUID" outType="xs:GUID"/> <data name="ErrorCode" inType="win:UInt32" outType="xs:unsignedInt"/> </template>

Event.Message: WCN received a message. Transport: %1 Message: %3
Event.Template: <template xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/win/2004/08/events"> <data name="Transport" inType="win:UnicodeString" outType="xs:string"/> <data name="TransportSubType" inType="win:UnicodeString" outType="xs:string"/> <data name="MessageGuid" inType="win:GUID" outType="xs:GUID"/> <data name="MessageBlobLength" inType="win:UInt16" outType="xs:unsignedShort"/> <data name="MessageBlob" inType="win:Binary" outType="xs:hexBinary" length="MessageBlobLength"/> </template>

Event.Message: WCN is sending a message. Transport: %1 Message: %3
Event.Template: <template xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/win/2004/08/events"> <data name="Transport" inType="win:UnicodeString" outType="xs:string"/> <data name="TransportSubType" inType="win:UnicodeString" outType="xs:string"/> <data name="MessageGuid" inType="win:GUID" outType="xs:GUID"/> <data name="MessageBlobLength" inType="win:UInt16" outType="xs:unsignedShort"/> <data name="MessageBlob" inType="win:Binary" outType="xs:hexBinary" length="MessageBlobLength"/> </template>

Event.Message: WCN has changed its beacons on transport %1
Event.Template: <template xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/win/2004/08/events"> <data name="Transport" inType="win:UnicodeString" outType="xs:string"/> <data name="MessageBlobLength" inType="win:UInt16" outType="xs:unsignedShort"/> <data name="MessageBlob" inType="win:Binary" outType="xs:hexBinary" length="MessageBlobLength"/> </template>

Event.Message: WCN has changed its probe response on transport %1
Event.Template: <template xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/win/2004/08/events"> <data name="Transport" inType="win:UnicodeString" outType="xs:string"/> <data name="MessageBlobLength" inType="win:UInt16" outType="xs:unsignedShort"/> <data name="MessageBlob" inType="win:Binary" outType="xs:hexBinary" length="MessageBlobLength"/> </template>
